 Q5-> Write a short note on the tab index

 ANS-
 The HTML tabindex attribute is used to manage keyboard focus. Used wisely, it can effectively handle focus within web widgets. 
 Used unwisely however, the tabindex attribute can destroy the usability of web content for keyboard users.

